title: [Ranger Guild, Jungle Approach]
description: Cinnamon-colored bark describes a path through the dense arbor.  Mangosteen trees, small in stature, give way to their taller banana and mango brethren.  Several stands of ferns grow in their shady boughs, while a flock of birds-of-paradise have lighted on the single sunny patch in the area.

Cinnamon-colored bark describes a trail through a dense arbor.  Mangosteen trees, small in stature, give way to their taller banana and mango brethren.  Several stands of ferns grow in their shady boughs and are just beyond the gentle touch of the silvery moonlight.
paths: Obvious paths: north, northeast, east, southeast, south, southwest, west, northwest
